    "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\" lang=\"en\" xml:lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=utf-8\" />\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"nofollow\" />\n<title>TIDRONE - Threat Group Cards: A Threat Actor Encyclopedia</title>\n<link href=\"/style.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" />\n</head>\n<body class=\"mbody\">\n<div class=\"logos\">\n<table border=\"0\"><tr><td><a href=\"https://www.etda.or.th\"><img src=\"/img/logo-etda.png\" height=\"50\" alt=\"ETDA\" title=\"Visit the ETDA website\" /></a></td>\n<td><font size=\"3\">สำนักงานพัฒนาธุรกรรมทางอิเล็กทรอนิกส์<br />Electronic Transactions Development Agency</font></td></tr></table>\n</div>\n<link href=\"/menubar.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" />\n<div id=\"menubar\">\n<ul>\n  <li>\n    <a href=\"/cgi-bin/listgroups.cgi\">Groups</a>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <a href=\"/cgi-bin/listtools.cgi\">Tools</a>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <a href=\"/cgi-bin/aptsearch.cgi\">Search</a>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <a href=\"/cgi-bin/aptstats.cgi\">Statistics</a>\n  </li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"graph\">\n<div class=\"gline\"><img src=\"/img/clear.gif\" width=\"1\" height=\"3\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n<div><img src=\"/img/report.jpg\" width=\"900\" alt=\"Report\" /></div>\n<a name=\"top\"></a>\n<div class=\"searchdiv\"><a href=\"/cgi-bin/aptsearch.cgi\" title=\"Search the database\" class=\"inlink\">Search</a></div>\n<div class=\"outermain\"><a href=\"/cgi-bin/aptgroups.cgi\" class=\"inlink\" title=\"Home\">Home</a> &gt; <a href=\"/cgi-bin/listgroups.cgi\" class=\"inlink\" title=\"List all groups\">List all groups</a> &gt; TIDRONE</div>\n<h1>Threat Group Cards: A Threat Actor Encyclopedia</h1>\n<div class=\"innermainov\">\n<h3><a href=\"/cgi-bin/showcard.cgi?u=19ad5f2a-ef83-40b0-a692-fe19702ac6b4\" title=\"Get permanent link to this card\" class=\"inlink\"><img src=\"/img/link.png\" height=\"16\" alt=\"Permanent link\" /></a> APT group: TIDRONE</h3>\n<table width=\"100%\" class=\"tborder\">\n<tr><td nowrap valign=\"top\" width=\"0%\" class=\"tshaded\">Names</td><td valign=\"top\" colspan=\"2\" width=\"100%\">TIDRONE <i><font size=\"-2\">",
    "</font></i></td></tr>\n<tr><td nowrap valign=\"top\" width=\"0%\" class=\"tshaded\">Country</td><td valign=\"top\" colspan=\"2\" width=\"100%\">[Unknown]</td></tr>\n<tr><td nowrap valign=\"top\" width=\"0%\" class=\"tshaded\">Motivation</td><td valign=\"top\" colspan=\"2\" width=\"100%\"><a href=\"/cgi-bin/listgroups.cgi?m=Information%20theft%20and%20espionage\" title=\"Search for all threat groups with motivation Information theft and espionage\" class=\"inlink\">Information theft and espionage</a></td></tr>\n<tr><td nowrap valign=\"top\" width=\"0%\" class=\"tshaded\">First seen</td><td valign=\"top\" colspan=\"2\" width=\"100%\">2024</td></tr>\n<tr><td nowrap valign=\"top\" width=\"0%\" class=\"tshaded\">Description</td><td valign=\"top\" colspan=\"2\" width=\"100%\">",
    "Since the beginning of 2024, we have been receiving incident response cases from Taiwan. We track this unidentified threat cluster as TIDRONE. Our research reveals that the threat actors have shown significant interest in military-related industry chains, particularly in the manufacturers of drones. Furthermore, telemetry from VirusTotal indicates that the targeted countries are varied; thus, everyone should stay vigilant of this threat.</td></tr>\n<tr><td nowrap valign=\"top\" width=\"0%\" class=\"tshaded\">Observed</td><td valign=\"top\" colspan=\"2\" width=\"100%\">Sectors: <a href=\"/cgi-bin/listgroups.cgi?s=Defense\" title=\"Search for all threat groups that target Defense\" class=\"inlink\">Defense</a>, <a href=\"/cgi-bin/listgroups.cgi?s=Telecommunications\" title=\"Search for all threat groups that target Telecommunications\" class=\"inlink\">Telecommunications</a>.<br />Countries: <a href=\"/cgi-bin/listgroups.cgi?v=South%20Korea\" title=\"Search for all threat groups that target South Korea\" class=\"inlink\">South Korea</a>, <a href=\"/cgi-bin/listgroups.cgi?v=Taiwan\" title=\"Search for all threat groups that target Taiwan\" class=\"inlink\">Taiwan</a>.</td></tr>\n<tr><td nowrap valign=\"top\" width=\"0%\" class=\"tshaded\">Tools used</td><td valign=\"top\" colspan=\"2\" width=\"100%\"><a href=\"/cgi-bin/listgroups.cgi?t=CLNTEND\" title=\"Search for all threat groups that use CLNTEND\" class=\"inlink\">CLNTEND</a>, <a href=\"/cgi-bin/listgroups.cgi?t=CXCLNT\" title=\"Search for all threat groups that use CXCLNT\" class=\"inlink\">CXCLNT</a>.</td></tr>\n<tr><td nowrap valign=\"top\" rowspan=\"1\" width=\"0%\" class=\"tshaded\">Operations performed</td><td nowrap valign=\"top\" width=\"0%\">2024</td><td valign=\"top\" width=\"100%\">Analysis on the Case of TIDRONE Threat Actor’s Attacks on Korean Companies<br />&lt;<a href=\"https://asec.ahnlab.com/en/85119/\" title=\"Follow external link\" class=\"exlink\" target=\"_blank\">https://asec.ahnlab.com/en/85119/</a>&gt;</td></tr>\n<tr><td nowrap valign=\"top\" width=\"0%\" class=\"tshaded\">Information</td><td valign=\"top\" colspan=\"2\" width=\"100%\">&lt;<a href=\"https://www.trendmicro.com/en_us/research/24/i/tidrone-targets-military-and-satellite-industries-in-taiwan.html\" title=\"Follow external link\" class=\"exlink\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.trendmicro.com/en_us/research/24/i/tidrone-targets-military-and-satellite-industries-in-taiwan.html</a>&gt;</td></tr>\n</table>\n<p>Last change to this card: 27 December 2024</p>\n<p>Download this actor card in <a href=\"/cgi-bin/getcard.cgi?g=TIDRONE&o=p\" title=\"Download this card in PDF format\" class=\"inlink\">PDF</a> or <a href=\"/cgi-bin/getcard.cgi?g=TIDRONE&o=j\" title=\"Download this card in JSON format\" class=\"inlink\">JSON</a> format</p>\n<div class=\"backtotop\"><a href=\"#top\" title=\"Back to the top\" class=\"inlink\">&uarr;</a></div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\">\n<tr><td width=\"80%\" rowspan=\"4\" valign=\"top\">\n<p>Infrastructure and Security Department<br />\nElectronic Transactions Development Agency</p>\n<h3>Follow us on</h3>\n<a href=\"https://facebook.com/ETDA.Thailand\"><img src=\"/img/icon-facebook.png\" alt=\"Facebook\" title=\"Follow us on Facebook\" /></a>\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/etda_thailand\"><img src=\"/img/icon-twitter.png\" alt=\"Twitter\" title=\"Follow us on Twitter\" /></a>\n</td><td colspan=\"2\">\n<h3>Report incidents</h3>\n</td>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"0%\"><img src=\"/img/icon-phone.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" alt=\"Telephone\" title=\"Telephone\" /></td>\n<td width=\"20%\"><strong>+66"
